        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-22 17:54:49   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1287791689100863610" id="quote-1287791689100863610" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1287791689100863610" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=175&amp;mid=1287791689100863610&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1287791689100863610&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1287791689100863610" onclick="followToggle('add','1287791689100863610')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
