      <div class="msgContentFrame">1. Yes the cap is split between the two classes you are using <br />- Sentinel and Gladiator (sword) <br />2. I have never received any amount of SP for taunting. <br />3. Yes we have a unreasonably slow SP gain, I've resorted to just using light slash/pierce and grinding low level mobs for what seems to be a skill up every 2 hrs.</div>
