      <div class="msgContentFrame">You get skill ups from taking hits, not from taunting.  In essence, the pugilist in your group was being a selfish douche.  If they're already close to capping SP earned/fight and someone in the group is taking it a step further and drawing off one of your options to earn SP, there's a problem in the attitude department that you might want to look into correcting with them.  Maybe FFXIV will shape up to be an exception, but I'm accustomed to a certain etiquette that says if you're not the designated tank, you don't do things like taunt unless the tank is dead.</div>
